creator: Tapps Games
descriptionHtml:
It’s lunch time! People are excited to visit your new burger shop and try the delicious hamburgers everyone has been talking about! Check the cooking game ingredients and get ready to serve the customers a delightful meal of their favorite recipes in sandwich games!

In My Burger Shop 2 you’ll run the hottest fast food restaurant in cooking game town. Manage to serve your clients with your restaurant’s tasty specialties: delicious hamburgers and cheeseburgers -- with extra cheese, onions, pickles, tomatoes and, of course, a lot of bacon! And what about some French fries? Complete the order with a refreshing drink, like in the best restaurant games!

Serve your sandwich games customers with an efficient dash games service to earn coins that you can use to buy new food games ingredients and other items to customize your shop. You can also unlock new dash games ingredients to make even more burgers and let your business grow.

COOKING GAME HIGHLIGHTS
🍔 Many sandwich games ingredients to choose from, just like in a real burger shop from restaurant games: bread, cheese, crispy burgers, chicken patties, lettuce, onions, pickles, even sausages and much more.
🍔 Customizable food games and dash games items to give the store the look you want
🍔 Serve weird and funny food games customers
🍔 Addictive time management and sandwich games gameplay

My Burger Shop 2 is the most fun time management, fast food restaurant and hamburger making game! Show off your dash games skills and turn your burger shop into a meaty business to rival the biggest restaurant games!

Start playing the most burger-ful of food games now!

Please note! This cooking game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and restaurant games extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.

It’s lunch time! People are excited to visit your new burger shop and try the delicious hamburgers everyone has been talking about! Check the cooking game ingredients and get ready to serve the customers a delightful meal of their favorite recipes in sandwich games!

In My Burger Shop 2 you’ll run the hottest fast food restaurant in cooking game town. Manage to serve your clients with your restaurant’s tasty specialties: delicious hamburgers and cheeseburgers -- with extra cheese, onions, pickles, tomatoes and, of course, a lot of bacon! And what about some French fries? Complete the order with a refreshing drink, like in the best restaurant games!

Serve your sandwich games customers with an efficient dash games service to earn coins that you can use to buy new food games ingredients and other items to customize your shop. You can also unlock new dash games ingredients to make even more burgers and let your business grow.

COOKING GAME HIGHLIGHTS
🍔 Many sandwich games ingredients to choose from, just like in a real burger shop from restaurant games: bread, cheese, crispy burgers, chicken patties, lettuce, onions, pickles, even sausages and much more.
🍔 Customizable food games and dash games items to give the store the look you want
🍔 Serve weird and funny food games customers
🍔 Addictive time management and sandwich games gameplay

My Burger Shop 2 is the most fun time management, fast food restaurant and hamburger making game! Show off your dash games skills and turn your burger shop into a meaty business to rival the biggest restaurant games!

Start playing the most burger-ful of food games now!

Please note! This cooking game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and restaurant games extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.
